  "instructions": [
    "Heat the oil in a large pan over medium heat",
    "Add the diced onion and cook until softened",
    "Add the diced carrots and celery and cook until they start to soften",
    "Add the mushrooms and cook until they release their moisture and start to brown",
    "Add the curry paste and cook for 1 minute",
    "Pour in the coconut milk and bring to a simmer",
    "Add the fish sauce, brown sugar, salt, and black pepper, and stir to combine",
    "Reduce the heat to low and let simmer for 10 minutes",
    "Serve hot over rice or noodles"
